values:
Whoa, much needed update. 0__o;;

......

Anyways, Angie's B-day ish coming up. I hear Loney's is too. Damn. X.X;;
I got yelled at the other day...So I'm a little scared to call Angela back as of right now. >.>;;

And well... I got fired from my job....as well. T.T
Apparently my boss, Mr. Pain. (Yes...that's his real name. @.@) saw me "Womanizing" the other day during work. -.-;;;
So..I was fired about 3 days ago...-.-;;
As if! Why the hell would I be womanizing if I have D-kun? Can't a guy be nice to <b>all</b> his customers?!
Awww, damn...I really liked working at the Ice skating ring. -.-;;
Hmmmmm...Well now I'm totally jobless. *cry*
Hmmmmm....Where to work next? Man it's been a while since I've been job hunting.
I ain't working at some greasey fast food joint ether! Blech! I was horrified when I decided to tag along with D-kun when he went to work at McDonald's. @.@;; Thank god I made him quit that job. The very sight of the crud would make anyone sick. That couldn't have been good for him...or me...guess what I ended up eatting before I entered the place. -.-;;
Even if he was making $8.50 an hour....which is indeed a lot...I must admit... >.<
More then what I made... 0__o;;
Wheee, D-kun's now working at WardenBook's....that store kicks ass! 
Even though D-kun wasn't 18...he still got the job....He gets to handle all the "Adult-rated" books. XD

.........
So I saw Mr.Pain today...XD
For some odd reason all these little boys were all hanging around him... 0__o;;
It was kinda creepy...I know none of them were his kids...considering I go to the same school with a few of his daughters....Man does he have a lot of daughters. >.>;; Damn are they Clingy...to me...damn... 0__o;; 
But anyways...I never did like working for him. >.<;;

Hmmm...oh yeah...And it's offical.
I'm rooming with my sister this coming November.
I'll be living life in Texas! Wheee! Only 300 miles away from my D-kun! ^^;;
Hehehe...about this time I won't end up dehydrating again. 0__o;;

How's that for an update? XD

PS) Yeah...My profile...hmmm, I've been sick for so long that I forgot where I stuck all my files. >.<
I'll have my matching Fai layout up soon....hopefully...Kay my little Taishi?
